#- Book 1: The Nigganing§0
§0
§0In the beginning, the§0
§0Hood was empty. No§0
§0Nigga walked the§0
§0streets; and no Hoe§0
§0was at a street§0
§0corner. No malt liqour§0
§0or tequila was sold.§0
§0
§0Times were dark.§0

#- But a light shone into§0
§0the Darkness. A Light§0
§0so Dark that he§0
§0instantly became§0
