#- Book 3: Savage§0
§0
§0Randy Savage took the word of Niggod to the White Folk of the world. Hoping to make them into Niggas. Sadly, the White Folk were weak in dick and could only become Wiggas. Almost Niggas, but dissapointing.
#- He dropped elbow after elbow upon the tracheas of the unfaithful, yet they never relented. It is known that around the time of the predicted Christian event of the Rapture, Macho Man entered the Long Sleep,
#- and punched the bitch-ass bringers of the apocalypse to their knees.§0
§0
