#- Book 5: Darkness Anew§0
§0
§0Niggolytes killed one another. They raped hoes rather than making them main and side bitches. Times were once again Dark. It was awful.§0

#- A Prophet was born.§0
§0A new Prophet, to spread the word§0
§0of Niggod anew. Darkness still persists, but Niggod will shine his Light and Tek9 into the faces of the world and say: "Roads are shit, Nigga."§0

